summary: AN ORDINANCE relating to land use and zoning; amending Chapter 23.32 of the Seattle Municipal Code at page 173 of the Official Land Use Map, to rezone property located at 3908 S. Kenyon St., from Lowrise 2 (L2) multifamily residential to Lowrise 4 (L4) multifamily residential and accepting a Property Use and Development Agreement in connection therewith. (Petition of Inter\*Im Community Development Association, C.F. 307757, Project Number 3003886)
